# Codex Runbook

This file is the required operating record for every Codex run in this
workspace. Read it together with `AGENTS.md` before changing files or running
simulation tasks.

## Workspace

Root workspace:

```text
/home/clcwork/UAV_capture/px4_ros2_ws
